title: #20 Dan Venticher Honey Creek Dairy
subtitle: #20 Dan Venticher Honey Creek Dairy
summary:
For part three of the dairy mini series we sat down with Dan Venticher from Honey Creek Dairy in North Eastern Iowa
Dan and his brother run a 190 cow dairy with feeding and milking robots!
